'''Halbeeg''' ([[ingiriis]]: Unit) waa cabir lagu [[xisaab|xisaabiyo]] dhamaan qiyaasaha ganacsiga iyo [[saynis]]ka; sida [[heerkul|heerkulka]], dhererka, xawaaraha, [[Wakhti|wakhtiga]], [[mug|muga]], [[cuf]]ka IWM. 

[[Duni]]da waxaa jira nidaam la iskugu geeyo dhamaan halbeegyada kaas oo loo yaqaano '''Nidaamka Caalamiga ee Halbeega''' (The International System of Units [loo soo gaabiyo [[SI]] oo laga soo xigtay erayga Faransiiska ah: Le Système
international d'unités) 

Guud ahaan waxaa jira tiro badan oo halbeegyo ah loona isticmaalo noocyo kala duwan, laakiin waxaa aasaas u ah dhamaantood [[Halbeeg|Todoba Halbeeg]] kuwaas oo kala ah: 

*[[Halbeeg]]a [[Heerkul]]ka, sida [[Salsiyas]], [[Kelfin]] iyo [[Fahrenhayt]]. 

*Halbeega [[Wakhti]]ga, sida [[Ilbiriqsi]], [[Daqiiqad]], [[Saacad]], [[Maalin]], [[Sanad]] iyo [[Qarni]]. 

*Halbeega [[Dherer]]ka, sida [[Centimetre|Sentimitir]], [[Mitir]], [[Kilomitir]], iyo [[Hectometre|Hektomitir]]. 

*Halbeega [[Mug|Miisaanka]] sida [[Kilo]], [[Kilogiram]], 

*Halbeega '''Kandhela''' 

*Halbeega '''Mole''' lagu qiyaaso [[Walax]]da, iyo 

*Halbeega [[Ambiyer]] oo lagu cabiro [[Koronto|Korontada]].

